name: Minute Till Crash Land
description:
Minute Till Crash Land

-----Lore-----

You are the pilot of a plane, which is running out of fuel. You only got fuel for a minute of flight time before you'll crash land. There's no land in sight, only ocean.

But! You got the power of magic on your side! You can spawn in enemy planes!

If you collide with any enemies, you will lose fuel.

But if you shoot down these enemy planes, you can take their supplies.

Supplies like more fuel, as well as cool powerups!

How long can you last? How many points can you collect?

-----Credits-----

All assets were created by me.

This game was made for the No Code Game Jam #2
